articles.author: The Associated Press
articles.title: Japan and Australia urge calm after Chinese radar locks on Japanese jets - NBC News
articles.description: TOKYO — Japan and Australia urged calm on Sunday after Chinese military aircraft locked radar on Japanese fighter jets, a month after the Japanese leader's recent remarks on Taiwan that stirred tensions between Tokyo and Beijing
